---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Cabinets partenaires — Bleu de Cobalt · Collectif Cobalt"
  description="Les cabinets partenaires du programme Bleu de Cobalt, réseau d'architectes en Nouvelle-Aquitaine."
  current="bleu-cabinets"
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="cab-hero">
    <div class="ch-bg-num" aria-hidden="true">B2B</div>
    <div class="sr">
      <div class="ch-eyebrow">Bleu de Cobalt — Missions · Cabinets</div>
      <h1 class="ch-title">RENFORT <em>cabinet</em>,<br />sans embaucher.</h1>
      <p class="ch-sub">Vous êtes un cabinet d'architecture en pic de charge, sur un concours, ou avec un livrable serré. Bleu vous place un alternant encadré, en mission courte, sans paperasse RH. Vous payez la mission, on gère le cadre.</p>
      <a href="#start" class="btn btn-cream"><span>Démarrer une mission →</span></a>
    </div>
    <div class="ch-stat-strip sr sr-d2">
      <div class="ch-stat">
        <div class="ch-stat-num">3 → 12</div>
        <div class="ch-stat-lbl">Semaines · durée mission</div>
        <div class="ch-stat-desc">Renouvelable. Vous engagez la mission, pas la personne.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ch-stat">
        <div class="ch-stat-num">7 jours</div>
        <div class="ch-stat-lbl">Délai de mise à dispo</div>
        <div class="ch-stat-desc">Brief reçu lundi, alternant matché et briefé sous une semaine.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ch-stat">
        <div class="ch-stat-num">0</div>
        <div class="ch-stat-lbl">Convention à rédiger</div>
        <div class="ch-stat-desc">Cadre associatif fourni par Bleu. Vous facturez Bleu, on facture l'alternant.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROBLEM -->
  <div class="pb-strip">
    <h2 class="pb-title sr">L'embauche, c'est trop. Le freelance senior, c'est trop cher.</h2>
    <p class="pb-body sr sr-d1">Vous avez un pic de production temporaire. <strong>Recruter un junior</strong> demande 6 semaines, du salaire annuel, et un risque RH. <strong>Un freelance confirmé</strong> coûte 500 à 800 €/jour. Bleu se positionne au milieu : <strong>un alternant encadré, briefé, supervisé</strong>, à un coût mission tenable, sans engagement.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- OFFRE -->
  <section class="offer">
    <div class="of-header sr">
      <h2 class="of-title">CE QU'ON FAIT <em>pour vous</em>.</h2>
      <p class="of-intro">Quatre types de missions courantes. Si votre besoin sort du cadre, écrivez-nous, on adapte.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="of-grid sr sr-d1">
      <div class="of-card">
        <div class="of-card-num">01</div>
        <h3 class="of-card-name">Production esquisse / APS</h3>
        <p class="of-card-desc">Plans, coupes, façades en phase amont. Pour répondre à un client, un concours, ou désengorger votre dessinateur principal.</p>
        <div class="of-card-meta">
          <div class="of-card-meta-item"><span class="of-card-meta-lbl">Durée</span><span class="of-card-meta-val">3 à 8 sem.</span></div>
          <div class="of-card-meta-item"><span class="of-card-meta-lbl">Profil</span><span class="of-card-meta-val">Bac +3 mini</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="of-card">
        <div class="of-card-num">02</div>
        <h3 class="of-card-name">Documents PRO / DCE</h3>
        <p class="of-card-desc">Plans techniques, détails 1:5, CCTP, suivi consultation entreprises. Tâches chronophages que vos chefs de projet n'ont plus le temps de faire.</p>
        <div class="of-card-meta">
          <div class="of-card-meta-item"><span class="of-card-meta-lbl">Durée</span><span class="of-card-meta-val">6 à 12 sem.</span></div>
          <div class="of-card-meta-item"><span class="of-card-meta-lbl">Profil</span><span class="of-card-meta-val">Bac +4/5</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="of-card">
        <div class="of-card-num">03</div>
        <h3 class="of-card-name">Modélisation 3D / Vues client</h3>
        <p class="of-card-desc">Modélisation Twinmotion, Lumion, Enscape. Production de vues pour présentation client ou dossier de permis.</p>
        <div class="of-card-meta">
          <div class="of-card-meta-item"><span class="of-card-meta-lbl">Durée</span><span class="of-card-meta-val">2 à 6 sem.</span></div>
          <div class="of-card-meta-item"><span class="of-card-meta-lbl">Profil</span><span class="of-card-meta-val">Bac +3 mini</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="of-card">
        <div class="of-card-num">04</div>
        <h3 class="of-card-name">Études matières / Recherches</h3>
        <p class="of-card-desc">Veille matériaux, fiches techniques, contact fournisseurs, montage moodboards. Travail amont qu'on n'a jamais le temps de faire bien.</p>
        <div class="of-card-meta">
          <div class="of-card-meta-item"><span class="of-card-meta-lbl">Durée</span><span class="of-card-meta-val">3 à 6 sem.</span></div>
          <div class="of-card-meta-item"><span class="of-card-meta-lbl">Profil</span><span class="of-card-meta-val">Bac +2 mini</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING -->
  <section class="pricing">
    <div class="pc-header sr">
      <h2 class="pc-title">BARÈME <em>public</em>.</h2>
      <p class="pc-intro">Tarif jour facturé à votre cabinet, encadrement Cobalt et indemnité alternant inclus. Pas de marge cachée — la grille est sur le site.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pc-table sr sr-d1">
      <div class="pc-cell head">Profil</div>
      <div class="pc-cell head">Tarif jour HT</div>
      <div class="pc-cell head">Forfait semaine</div>
      <div class="pc-cell head">Forfait mois</div>

      <div class="pc-cell"><div class="pc-cell-name">Junior · Bac +2/3</div><div class="pc-cell-sub">BTS, L3, première mission</div></div>
      <div class="pc-cell"><div class="pc-cell-val">220 €<small>jour</small></div></div>
      <div class="pc-cell"><div class="pc-cell-val">1 000 €<small>5 jours</small></div></div>
      <div class="pc-cell"><div class="pc-cell-val">3 600 €<small>~20 jours</small></div></div>

      <div class="pc-cell"><div class="pc-cell-name">Confirmé · Bac +4</div><div class="pc-cell-sub">Master 1, plusieurs missions au compteur</div></div>
      <div class="pc-cell"><div class="pc-cell-val">280 €<small>jour</small></div></div>
      <div class="pc-cell"><div class="pc-cell-val">1 280 €<small>5 jours</small></div></div>
      <div class="pc-cell"><div class="pc-cell-val">4 600 €<small>~20 jours</small></div></div>

      <div class="pc-cell"><div class="pc-cell-name">Senior · Bac +5</div><div class="pc-cell-sub">Master 2, autonome sur livrable PRO</div></div>
      <div class="pc-cell"><div class="pc-cell-val">340 €<small>jour</small></div></div>
      <div class="pc-cell"><div class="pc-cell-val">1 550 €<small>5 jours</small></div></div>
      <div class="pc-cell"><div class="pc-cell-val">5 600 €<small>~20 jours</small></div></div>
    </div>
    <p class="pc-note">Pour comparer : un freelance confirmé sur le marché tourne à 500-800 € jour. Une embauche junior coûte ~3 200 € chargés / mois en CDI, hors recrutement. Bleu se cale entre les deux, sans engagement long.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- PROCESS -->
  <section class="process">
    <h2 class="pr-title sr">DE LA DEMANDE <em>à l'alternant en poste</em>.</h2>
    <div class="pr-steps">
      <div class="pr-step sr">
        <div class="pr-step-bar"></div>
        <div class="pr-step-num">01</div>
        <div class="pr-step-name">Brief</div>
        <p class="pr-step-desc">Vous nous décrivez la mission : périmètre, livrable, durée, démarrage souhaité. Formulaire ou appel 15 min.</p>
        <div class="pr-step-time">Jour 0</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pr-step sr sr-d1">
        <div class="pr-step-bar"></div>
        <div class="pr-step-num">02</div>
        <div class="pr-step-name">Matching</div>
        <p class="pr-step-desc">On vous propose 1 à 2 profils dans la journée. Vous choisissez sur portfolio + 30 min visio.</p>
        <div class="pr-step-time">J+2</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pr-step sr sr-d2">
        <div class="pr-step-bar"></div>
        <div class="pr-step-num">03</div>
        <div class="pr-step-name">Conventionnement</div>
        <p class="pr-step-desc">Convention de mission Bleu ↔ cabinet, simple, 2 pages. Démarrage validé.</p>
        <div class="pr-step-time">J+4</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pr-step sr sr-d3">
        <div class="pr-step-bar"></div>
        <div class="pr-step-num">04</div>
        <div class="pr-step-name">Prise de poste</div>
        <p class="pr-step-desc">L'alternant démarre chez vous (ou en distant). Référent Cobalt en lien hebdo. Vous facturez Bleu chaque mois.</p>
        <div class="pr-step-time">J+7</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- START -->
  <section id="start" class="start">
    <div class="st-grid">
      <div class="sr">
        <div class="st-eyebrow">Démarrer une mission</div>
        <h2 class="st-title">Décrivez la mission, <em>on revient sous 48 h</em>.</h2>
        <p class="st-body">Pas besoin de brief ultra cadré. Une phrase sur le contexte, une sur le besoin, votre durée, votre démarrage souhaité. On revient avec 1 à 2 profils.</p>
        <p class="st-body" style="font-size:.85rem; color:rgba(26,26,26,.55)">Ou écrivez directement à <strong style="color:var(--noir)">bleu@collectifcobalt.eu</strong>.</p>
      </div>
      <form class="st-form sr sr-d1" id="st-form-cab">
        <div class="st-field"><label class="st-lbl">Cabinet · contact</label><input class="st-input" type="text" placeholder="Cabinet X · Camille Dupont" required /></div>
        <div class="st-field"><label class="st-lbl">Email pro</label><input class="st-input" type="email" placeholder="camille@cabinet-x.fr" required /></div>
        <div class="st-field"><label class="st-lbl">Mission en deux phrases</label><textarea class="st-ta" placeholder="Concours équipement public, besoin de production esquisse + 8 vues 3D. 6 semaines, démarrage juin." required></textarea></div>
        <div class="st-field"><label class="st-lbl">Démarrage souhaité</label><input class="st-input" type="text" placeholder="Sous 2 semaines · juin 2026 · etc." required /></div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark" style="margin-top:8px; align-self:flex-start"><span>Envoyer la demande →</span></button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MARQUEE -->
  <div class="marquee-wrap">
    <div class="marquee-track">
      <div class="marquee-item">RENFORT CABINET<div class="marquee-sep"></div></div>
      <div class="marquee-item"><span class="hi" style="color:var(--jaune)">SANS RH</span><div class="marquee-sep"></div></div>
      <div class="marquee-item">7 JOURS<div class="marquee-sep"></div></div>
      <div class="marquee-item"><span class="hi" style="color:var(--jaune)">MISSIONS COURTES</span><div class="marquee-sep"></div></div>
      <div class="marquee-item">BLEU DE COBALT<div class="marquee-sep"></div></div>
      <div class="marquee-item"><span class="hi" style="color:var(--jaune)">220 → 340 € / JOUR</span><div class="marquee-sep"></div></div>
      <div class="marquee-item">RENFORT CABINET<div class="marquee-sep"></div></div>
      <div class="marquee-item"><span class="hi" style="color:var(--jaune)">SANS RH</span><div class="marquee-sep"></div></div>
      <div class="marquee-item">7 JOURS<div class="marquee-sep"></div></div>
      <div class="marquee-item"><span class="hi" style="color:var(--jaune)">MISSIONS COURTES</span><div class="marquee-sep"></div></div>
      <div class="marquee-item">BLEU DE COBALT<div class="marquee-sep"></div></div>
      <div class="marquee-item"><span class="hi" style="color:var(--jaune)">220 → 340 € / JOUR</span><div class="marquee-sep"></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<script is:inline>
  const f = document.getElementById('st-form-cab');
  if (f) f.addEventListener('submit', (e) => { e.preventDefault(); alert('Merci ! Réponse sous 48 h.'); });
</script>

<style is:global>
  .stripe { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--jaune) 25%, var(--noir) 25% 50%, var(--jaune) 50% 75%, var(--noir) 75%); }

  /* HERO */
  .cab-hero {
    background: var(--noir); padding: 140px 44px 90px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: end; min-height: 80vh;
  }
  .ch-bg-num {
    position: absolute; right: -40px; bottom: -60px;
    font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: clamp(260px,32vw,420px);
    color: rgba(241,203,79,.06); line-height: 1; pointer-events: none; user-select: none;
  }
  .ch-eyebrow { font-size: .62rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--jaune); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .ch-eyebrow::before { content: ''; width: 24px; height: 2px; background: var(--jaune); }
  .ch-title { font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: clamp(56px,9vw,140px); line-height: .82; color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .ch-title em { font-family: var(--f-serif); font-style: italic; color: var(--jaune); font-weight: 400; }
  .ch-sub { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.85; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(240,235,216,.55); margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .ch-stat-strip {
    background: rgba(241,203,79,.07); border: 1px solid rgba(241,203,79,.15);
    border-radius: var(--r-md); padding: 30px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px;
  }
  .ch-stat { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 4px; padding-bottom: 22px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(241,203,79,.18); }
  .ch-stat:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
  .ch-stat-num { font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: 38px; color: var(--jaune); line-height: 1; }
  .ch-stat-lbl { font-size: .68rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(240,235,216,.55); }
  .ch-stat-desc { font-size: .8rem; line-height: 1.55; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(240,235,216,.4); margin-top: 6px; }

  /* PROBLEM */
  .pb-strip {
    background: var(--jaune); padding: 70px 44px;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--noir);
  }
  .pb-title { font-family: var(--f-serif); font-style: italic; font-size: clamp(2.5rem,4vw,4rem); line-height: 1; color: var(--noir); }
  .pb-body { font-size: .95rem; line-height: 1.85; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(26,26,26,.7); }
  .pb-body strong { font-weight: 700; color: var(--noir); }

  /* OFFRE */
  .offer { background: var(--cream); padding: 100px 44px; border-top: 2px solid var(--noir); }
  .of-header { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: end; margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .of-title { font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: clamp(48px,7vw,100px); line-height: .88; }
  .of-title em { font-family: var(--f-serif); font-style: italic; color: var(--jaune); font-weight: 400; }
  .of-intro { font-size: .92rem; line-height: 1.85; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(26,26,26,.6); }
  .of-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); gap: 18px; }
  .of-card {
    background: var(--cream); border: 1.5px solid var(--noir); border-radius: var(--r-md);
    padding: 36px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;
    transition: background .25s;
  }
  .of-card:hover { background: rgba(241,203,79,.12); }
  .of-card-num { font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: 38px; color: var(--jaune); line-height: 1; }
  .of-card-name { font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.05; color: var(--noir); }
  .of-card-desc { font-size: .9rem; line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(26,26,26,.6); }
  .of-card-meta { display: flex; gap: 16px; padding-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(26,26,26,.12); margin-top: auto; }
  .of-card-meta-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
  .of-card-meta-lbl { font-size: .55rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(26,26,26,.45); }
  .of-card-meta-val { font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: 14px; color: var(--noir); }

  /* PRICING */
  .pricing { background: var(--noir); padding: 100px 44px; }
  .pc-header { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: end; margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .pc-title { font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: clamp(48px,7vw,100px); line-height: .88; color: var(--cream); }
  .pc-title em { font-family: var(--f-serif); font-style: italic; color: var(--jaune); font-weight: 400; }
  .pc-intro { font-size: .92rem; line-height: 1.85; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(240,235,216,.55); }
  .pc-table {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(240,235,216,.12); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(240,235,216,.12);
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 0;
  }
  .pc-cell { padding: 32px 28px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(240,235,216,.12); }
  .pc-cell:nth-child(4n) { border-right: none; }
  .pc-cell.head { font-size: .58rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(241,203,79,.7); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(240,235,216,.12); }
  .pc-cell-name { font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: 16px; color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .pc-cell-sub { font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(240,235,216,.4); line-height: 1.5; }
  .pc-cell-val { font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: 24px; color: var(--jaune); }
  .pc-cell-val small { font-family: var(--f-body); font-size: .58rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(240,235,216,.4); display: block; margin-top: 4px; }
  .pc-note { font-family: var(--f-serif); font-style: italic; font-size: .9rem; color: rgba(240,235,216,.55); margin-top: 32px; max-width: 760px; }

  /* PROCESS */
  .process { background: var(--cream); padding: 100px 44px; border-top: 2px solid var(--noir); }
  .pr-title { font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: clamp(48px,7vw,100px); line-height: .88; margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .pr-title em { font-family: var(--f-serif); font-style: italic; color: var(--jaune); font-weight: 400; }
  .pr-steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 0; border-top: 2px solid var(--noir); }
  .pr-step { padding: 40px 28px; border-right: 2px solid var(--noir); }
  .pr-step:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .pr-step-num { font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: 44px; color: rgba(241,203,79,.4); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .pr-step-bar { width: 28px; height: 3px; background: var(--jaune); margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .pr-step-name { font-size: .82rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--noir); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .pr-step-desc { font-size: .82rem; line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(26,26,26,.55); }
  .pr-step-time { font-family: var(--f-serif); font-style: italic; font-size: .82rem; color: rgba(26,26,26,.5); margin-top: 12px; }

  /* START */
  .start { background: var(--jaune); padding: 100px 44px; border-top: 2px solid var(--noir); }
  .st-grid { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: center; }
  .st-eyebrow { font-size: .62rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--noir); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .st-eyebrow::before { content: ''; width: 24px; height: 2px; background: var(--noir); }
  .st-title { font-family: var(--f-display); font-size: clamp(40px,5vw,64px); line-height: .9; color: var(--noir); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .st-title em { font-family: var(--f-serif); font-style: italic; color: var(--cream); font-weight: 400; }
  .st-body { font-size: .92rem; line-height: 1.85; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(26,26,26,.7); margin-bottom: 22px; }
  .st-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 18px; background: var(--cream); padding: 40px; border-radius: var(--r-md); border: 1.5px solid var(--noir); }
  .st-field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .st-lbl { font-size: .58rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(26,26,26,.5); }
  .st-input, .st-ta {
    background: transparent; border: none; border-bottom: 1.5px solid rgba(26,26,26,.2);
    padding: 10px 0; font-family: var(--f-body); font-size: .92rem;
    color: var(--noir); outline: none; transition: border-color .2s;
  }
  .st-ta { resize: none; min-height: 70px; }
  .st-input:focus, .st-ta:focus { border-color: var(--jaune); border-bottom-width: 2px; }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .cab-hero { padding: 110px 20px 60px; min-height: 0; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; }
    .ch-title { font-size: clamp(48px, 12vw, 90px); }
    .ch-sub { font-size: .92rem; }
    .pb-strip { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 28px; padding: 56px 20px; }
    .pb-title { font-size: clamp(2rem, 8vw, 3rem); }
    .offer { padding: 64px 20px; }
    .of-header { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 22px; margin-bottom: 36px; }
    .of-title { font-size: clamp(36px, 10vw, 64px); }
    .of-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
